{"tid":1830993,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[杯葛家有囍事]黃百鳴被揭2014年賀歲片收益捐幫港出聲","createTime":"2020-01-20T05:17:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T08:40:34.000Z","uid":21141,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6bc6fa393358356c60029caaa9864b869e344372","tid":1830993,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:17:10.000Z","msg":"全城杯葛藍絲電影人黃百鳴賀歲片《家有囍事2020》呼聲不斷，近日再被翻舊賬，六年前把賀歲片《六福囍事》首映場收益80萬捐予親中組織「幫港出聲」，及公開反對佔領中環，引起高登網民不滿引發罷看，最終《六福囍事》在衆多本地賀歲片票房「包尾」，收入僅1816萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wJs6M8p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwJs6M8p.jpg&h=9c38f7c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n市民翻查親中電影人黃百鳴媚共劣跡，發現2014年「佔中」爆發前，公開表明「反佔中」立場，形容中環為香港的心臟，「有人有問題回去整容、豐胸、洗腸搞乜都好，但係心臟唔搞得，因爲一搞可能會訓低」。又稱「只要和平、和氣、合理同合法」他就會支持，亦不會擔心票房收入會因自己政治取向受影響。其後黃百鳴宣佈將賀歲片《六福囍事》首映場收益80萬，捐給親中團體「幫港出聲」，並揚言支持政改。<br />\n<br />\n言論一出，令當時高登網民群起反之，呼籲罷看《六福囍事》，並嘲諷黃百鳴「心臟論」無知，不知道有心臟手術存在，「傻的嗎黃百鳴，通波仔、搭橋咪係攪（搞）個心臟」，又指其戲路越趨單調無聊，「免費都唔睇又何來杯葛」。結果當年賀歲片票房中，《六福》屬本地四套賀歲片最低，敗於《金雞SSS》、《西遊記之大鬧天宮》、《賭城風雲》，本地收入只有1816萬。<br />\n<br />\n黃百鳴年初一上映新片《家有囍事2020》，門徒事工強烈呼籲，港人齊心抵制「藍色電影」，要令票房差過《六福囍事》，遭到懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://apostlesmedia.com/20200118/24202\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapostlesmedia.com%2F20200118%2F24202&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BPzcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=29230222\" target=\"_blank\">https://apostlesmedia.com/20200118/24202</a><br />\n<br />\n罷睇有理！杯葛無罪！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f0894fbe66db6c906be64c66ddd006864d9f43","tid":1830993,"uid":21141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:17:42.000Z","msg":"田少條牆頭草又係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a542f899ef3c9472dbbe00a4358f409aa6ef143","tid":1830993,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:18:18.000Z","msg":"睇王晶黃百鳴等於捐錢去黑社會"},{"pid":"f50ceb25d8555211466bd6d1a50d9464fb53915a","tid":1830993,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5259f175b68fd16f369af3eeb72879033764a56","tid":1830993,"uid":249994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:20:18.000Z","msg":"去Cinema City 等於奶黃百鳴春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d459a4316e928b91d7309285f16b355bba8b14","tid":1830993,"uid":47239,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:21:00.000Z","msg":"就算唔講政治，講質素，家有喜事2020都收皮啦<br />\n又係大堆頭做埋啲on9劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntrailer都無笑點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5baeaa4660b446bcdc6183aa62f23439fae7a560","tid":1830993,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:46:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65e292139946cbdfa22761b490278486fd4d190a","tid":1830993,"uid":16672,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:54:58.000Z","msg":"故事簡介<br />\n<br />\n游永富（黃百鳴飾)、游永忠（張智霖飾)、游永馳（張繼聰飾）三兄弟表面是尋常人家,實際為精通千術的業餘俠盜,所得款項會作慈善用途。機緣巧合下,三兄弟遇上了老千姊妹花：雷夢娜（周秀娜飾）及雷夢露（陳靜飾），原來雷氏姊妹亦為俠盜，大家惺惺相惜，姊妹花亦搬入游家互相照應。 在一次意外中，兩家人得知城中富商鱷魚譚(譚耀文飾)實為作惡多端的黑幫頭目,決定聯手佈局儆惡懲奸。過程中人人扮鬼扮馬，合作過程亦令眾人的感情得以火速滋長,為游家帶來了連環囍事。<br />\n<br />\n2020年都仲玩緊食字既人名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0defe7f38c15e163160c57269320c1254230e22a","tid":1830993,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:55:19.000Z","msg":"不意外<br />\n捐錢俾星火先好出新聞啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc16a564f5d4b719c7046d0a44c79df84a48359c","tid":1830993,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T07:56:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5dcf32ef7cd078d0b02c076a0852af3d33af7bef","tid":1830993,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:03:20.000Z","msg":"文宣要宣傳吓"},{"pid":"276a687befd8144776313a66c3307b8370027160","tid":1830993,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:07:58.000Z","msg":"2014<br />\n仲有田少"},{"pid":"13a79623791bd4424a8d2fe42bcbd85f2b16eff8","tid":1830993,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:38:49.000Z","msg":"堆"},{"pid":"f2887e3ca2d92803ef4933b152c70fa47a3f9343","tid":1830993,"uid":37759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:40:34.000Z","msg":"就算冇政治原因，正常少少既香港人都唔會去睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}